Class TreeNode

java.lang.Object
com.example.full_connection.Model.TreeNode
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class TreeNode extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a node in a regression tree. Can be either a decision node or a leaf node with a prediction value.
